org.jcvi.jillion.sam.header

Class SamVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jcvi.jillion.sam.header.SamVersion

  • public final class SamVersion
extends Object
    SamVersion is an object representation of how which version of the SAM format the SAM file is encoded in.

    dkatzel

      • isBefore

        public boolean isBefore(SamVersion other)
        Is this SamVersion before the other given version. A version is before if either:
        1. This major field is less than the other major field
        2. The major versions are equal but this minor field is less than the other minor field.
        Parameters:
        other - the other version to compare to; can not be null.
        Returns:
        true if this version is before (meets the criteria stated above); false otherwise.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if other is null.

      • isAfter

        public boolean isAfter(SamVersion other)
        Is this SamVersion after the other given version. A version is after if either:
        1. This major field is greater than the other major field
        2. The major versions are equal but this minor field is greater than the other minor field.
        Parameters:
        other - the other version to compare to; can not be null.
        Returns:
        true if this version is after (meets the criteria stated above); false otherwise.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if other is null.

      • parseVersion

        public static SamVersion parseVersion(String versionStr)
        Parse a SAM version string (which is encoded in a SAM file header) into a SamVersion object.
        Parameters:
        versionStr - the sam version string to parse; can not be null.
        Returns:
        a new SamVersion instance if the versionStr is a valid SAM version pattern or null if it is not.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if versionStr is null.
